  <description>
    A simple version of the Royal Caribbean Brochure Planner Tool
  </description>

  <author href="https://plus.google.com/+FreddyJoanTorresBrandy" email="joanxtb@gmail.com">
    Freddy Joan Torres Brandy
  </author>  

